Source: x265
Version: 3.4
Port-Version: 3
Homepage: https://github.com/videolan/x265
Description: x265 is a H.265 / HEVC video encoder application library, designed to encode video or images into an H.265 / HEVC encoded bitstream.

Feature: hbd
Description: Store pixel samples as 16bit values (Main10/Main12)

Feature: main12
Build-Depends: x265[core,hbd]
Description: Support Main12 instead of Main10

Feature: hdr10plus
Description: Enable HDR10 Plus
